T06TD4074E:126b-1: yo ga aa ba ta ra /
T06TD4074E:127a-1: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T06TD4074E:127a-2: bstan bcos rgya chen bo ni thos nas kyang /
T06TD4074E:127a-3: don dam de bzhin nyid ni nges byas la //
T06TD4074E:127a-4: dad ldan de ni 'jam pa'i stan gnas te /
T06TD4074E:127a-5: blo dang ldan pas rnal 'byor brtson par bya /
T06TD4074E:127a-6: gzung dang 'dzin dang gnyi ga gnyis min dang /
T06TD4074E:127a-7: bdag dang gzhan dang mya ngan 'das pa dang //
T06TD4074E:127a-8: 'khor ba zhes bya'i rnam rtog mang po ni //
T06TD4074E:127a-9: rtag tu spangs la yid ni mnyam par gzhag / sgyu ma dri za'i grong khyer lta bu ni //
T06TD4074E:127a-10: shes bya ma lus rnam par bltas nas su //
T06TD4074E:127a-11: de bzhin nyid kyi ye shes rdo rje yis //
T06TD4074E:127a-12: lus kyi 'khrul 'khor rab tu gzhig par bya //
T06TD4074E:127a-13: rnam pa thams cad du ni rab mdzes la //
T06TD4074E:127a-14: thog dang tha ma'i cha bral rnam mi rtog //
T06TD4074E:127a-15: dri ma med pa'i 'od zer stong gis ni //
T06TD4074E:127a-16: mun pa nges bsal mkha' dang mtshungs pa yin //
T06TD4074E:127a-17: rang gi snang ba tsam gyi ngo bo ru //
T06TD4074E:127a-18: gzod nas skye ba med pa'i rang sems mthong //
T06TD4074E:127a-19: gang gis kyang ni de mthong gyur pa dag / de yang de bzhin du ni blta bar bya //
T06TD4074E:127a-20: dmigs pa med dang bcas pa'i sems nyid ni //
T06TD4074E:127a-21: de bzhin nyid dang yang dag mtha' ru bshad //
T06TD4074E:127a-22: de ltar rim gyis bslabs par gyur pa las //
T06TD4074E:127a-23: ming du shes pa 'gog pa 'thob par 'gyur //
T06TD4074E:127a-24: de la yang dag reg par sbyor ba las //
T06TD4074E:127a-25: 'bad pa med par mngon shes lnga ru 'gyur //
T06TD4074E:127a-26: de dang mngon par ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
T06TD4074E:127a-27: 'gro ba'i don ni dpag tu med par byed //
T06TD4074E:127a-28: 'di ni yongs su rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
T06TD4074E:127a-29: shin tu yun ring dus su gnas par 'gyur //
T06TD4074E:127a-30: lus ni rdo rje lta bur mi shig shing //
T06TD4074E:127a-31: nyon mongs bdud la sogs pas g-yo mi 'gyur //
T06TD4074E:127a-32: shes rab pha rol phyin pa zhes bya yi //
T06TD4074E:127a-33: rnal 'byor 'di dag rtag tu rab ldan pa //
T06TD4074E:127a-34: nam mkha' mdzod la sogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin //
T06TD4074E:127a-35: mang po rnams ni yang dag rdzogs par 'gyur //
T06TD4074E:127a-36: bdag gi rnal 'byor pa ni 'jug pa tsam //
T06TD4074E:127a-37: yang dag sbyar bas dge ba gang bsags pa //
T06TD4074E:127a-38: der ni 'gro ba thams cad rab myur ba //
T06TD4074E:127a-39: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes thob par shog //
T06TD4074E:127b-0: rnal 'byor la 'jug @127b pa zhes bya ba //
T06TD4074E:127b-1: slob dpon phyogs kyi glang po'i zhal snga nas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T06TD4074E:127b-3: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po dha rmma shr'i bha dra dang /
T06TD4074E:127b-4: lo ts'a ba dge slong rin chen bzang pos bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa /
